Definition: a form of behavior therapy in which a survivor confronts feelings or phobias or anxieties about a traumatic event and relives it in the therapy situation
Synonyms: desensitization_technique, a, form, of, behavior, therapy, in, which, survivor, confronts, feelings, or, phobias, anxieties, about, traumatic, event, and, relives, it, the, situation
Category: noun.act
